_sText:
surf_whirlpool
by So_NooB and [B]enj.
____________

Map made for 64 players.
Poison_remix HD skybox made by BD|RAjAN.
____________

There are 2 jails.
The first is a knifing jail, it opens every 30 seconds.
The second is a hegrenade jail, it opens if everyone push the button.
____________

You can have a lot of weapons on the map :
Deagle,Bullpup,Galil,Ak47,M4a1,Scout,Awp, Rifles, M3, M249, and a lot of others.
____________

It took me 1 week to make the map, with [B]enj helping.
____________

Hope you will enjoy this map.
Don't be affraid to comment and rate, thank you.
Have fun !

___________
